{
  "stem": "1338.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, in the forest outside of the open field, there were sitting the young German, what they call it, the home guard or whatever they were.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were shooting with machine guns.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he says to me, you see?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I told you, you will be back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- so anyway-- different people, different things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we got to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Buchenwald they-- Buchenwald was Czechish-run, wonderful place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, the first thing they ask us is, who was cruel?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Who was dead?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Who should be liquidated?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, it was very interesting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really fell in love with the Czechs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's why I stayed after the war in Prague.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I thought that they were really the most liberal, and the most civilized people of all the Eastern populations that I knew, again, statistically speaking.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some of my best friends are everywhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "By the way, I never raised a hand at another German.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was in Czechoslovakia after the war and they asked me to participate in beating Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I would never raise a hand against a German, because I would never know whether one of them could be Leib.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it still applies to this very day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we should never make any-- anti-Semitism is exactly what it is.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's classification of a-- whether right or wrong.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's always grouping.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "People should never fall into that-- that trap, ever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, anyway-- so in Buchenwald, they told us to-- all the Jews come out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, Serge said to me, are you crazy?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, when I came to the new camp, they ask you for your name.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I adopted my name [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Grad, ?] which is my mother's maiden name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At Buchenwald?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "AT Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
